Package gobblin.data.management.retention.version.finder

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VersionFinder<T extends DatasetVersion>
    Finds dataset versions in the file system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatasetVersionFinder<T extends DatasetVersion>
    Class to find dataset versions in the file system.
    DateTimeDatasetVersionFinder
    DatasetVersionFinder for datasets based on path timestamps.
    FileLevelTimestampVersionFinder
    VersionFinder that uses the most nested file, or directory if no file exists, level modifiedTimestamp under the datasetRoot path to find DatasetVersions, and represents each version as TimestampedDatasetVersion using the file level path and modifiedTimestamp.
    ModDateTimeDatasetVersionFinder
    VersionFinder for datasets based on modification timestamps.
    SingleVersionFinder
    Implementation of VersionFinder that uses a StringDatasetVersion and simply creates a single StringDatasetVersion for the given CleanableDataset.
    UnixTimestampVersionFinder
    Implementation of VersionFinder that generates TimestampedDatasetVersion from a unix timestamp in the name of each version path.
    WatermarkDatasetVersionFinder
    Finds watermarked dataset versions as direct subdirectories of the dataset directory.
